Anna Wintour: Met Ball 2012 with daughter Bee Shaffer 
2012-05-08 08:22:26 GMT
Anna Wintour hits the red carpet in Prada at the 2012 Met Ball held at the Metropolitan Museum of Art on Monday (May 7) in New York City.The 62-year-old Vogue editor-in-chief was joined at the annual gala by her daughter Bee Shaffer (in Erdem).Earlier in the day, Anna attended the press preview of the exhibit.This year’s Costume Institute Gala Benefit – celebrating the opening of the Schiaparelli and Prada: Impossible Conversations exhibition – is co-chaired by Carey Mulligan, Anna, and designer Miuccia Prada. 
